Trade/Device Name(s): Ensol EnTM Specimen Collection and Transport System
Document Summary: FDA 510(k) summary for Ensol EnTM Specimen Collection and Transport System for safe collection and transport of upper respiratory virus specimens using viral transport medium.
Indications for Use Summary: Intended for the collection and transportation of clinical samples containing upper respiratory viruses including Influenza A, Human Coronavirus 229E, and RSV from collection site to testing laboratory for use with standard diagnostic/identification techniques utilizing stable recoverable infectious viral particles.
